      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL REMARK (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.20) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 14 races. Better than last start and worth following up. BRAX KEEPING (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 30.28 beating Oakee Bear. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Sure to measure up. FASCINATE SAMUEL (4) missed the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 520m at this track in 29.80. Has the ability and looks a key chance. GOOFY ETHICS (8) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
